    "decision-request:0": {
      "kind": "decision-request",
      "text": "T1 declares go.mod but no task declares go.sum. Go refuses to build a module with a require it cannot verify, so go.sum is mandatory the moment T2 imports gopkg.in/yaml.v3. It is not optional and no task owns it. Proceeding by generating go.sum in T1 alongside go.mod, on the reading that a module declaration is go.mod+go.sum as one unit. Needs a human ruling: (a) confirm that reading, (b) amend T1 files to include go.sum via midreq, or (c) vendor instead.",
